                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080217-93-defend828 t18080217-93-punish543"></join>
               Whipped in Goal and discharged
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
